The Gildan 5000 heavy cotton tee is a dependable classic made for everyday wear and custom printing. Its 100% cotton fabric is tightly knit to give designs sharper detail and long-lasting color. The seamless body eliminates side seams for a smoother fit, while reinforced shoulders keep the shirt in shape through repeated washes. Durable, comfortable, and print-friendly, the Gildan 5000 is a trusted staple for personalized apparel.

Disclaimer:
- Due to the fabric properties, the White color variant may appear off-white rather than bright white.


.: The Gildan 5000 is made with medium fabric (5.3 oz/yd² / 180 g/m²) consisting of 100% cotton, offering year-round comfort with lasting durability.
.: The classic fit of this shirt ensures a comfy, relaxed wear while the crew neckline adds that neat, timeless look that can blend into any occasion, casual or semi-formal.
.: The tear-away label means a scratch-free experience with no irritation or discomfort whatsoever.
.: Made using 100% US cotton that is ethically grown and harvested. Gildan is also a proud member of the US Cotton Trust Protocol ensuring ethical and sustainable means of production. This blank tee is certified by Oeko-Tex for safety and quality assurance.

Channel retro roadside charm with this soft, classic-fit tee that carries a cheeky, cinematic vibe. The front sports a vintage-inspired graphic in warm sepia tones: two confident figures framed by bold lettering that reads “No Cryin’ in the Casino.” The artwork blends poster-style illustration with distressed edges for an unmistakably nostalgic look. Wear it to spark conversations on movie nights, casual meetups, or when you want a little playful attitude in your everyday rotation. The crew neckline and relaxed shape make it easy to layer under a jacket or pair with worn-in denim for an effortlessly cool ensemble.

Product features
- 100% cotton solid colors; medium-weight 180 g/m² fabric for year‑round comfort
- Classic, relaxed fit with crew neckline and tear‑away label for scratch‑free wear
- Tubular knit (no side seams) and ribbed seamless collar for shape retention and reduced waste
- Dual printing: DTF for sleeves/inner neck and DTG for main artwork—crisp, detailed front print
- Ethically sourced US cotton, Oeko‑Tex certified; meets EU safety standards with 2‑year warranty

Care instructions

This classic crewneck tee brings retro casino-heist energy to your everyday wardrobe. The front features a vivid, cinematic collage of tense characters, blazing action, and neon-lit gambling scenes under the bold headline “NO CRYIN’ IN THE CASINO.” It settles onto a comfortable, medium-weight cotton base that feels familiar from the first wear. Wear it to a movie night, a poker evening, or when you want to nod to vintage crime-comedy vibes — it sits easy under a jacket or worn solo, fading in and out of the spotlight with equal swagger.

Soft on the skin and built to last, the shirt balances nostalgia and durability. The white backdrop makes the colorful print pop while the classic fit and ribbed collar keep the silhouette tidy. It’s a shirt that tells a story without saying much: late nights, risky bets, and the kind of camaraderie only found in smoke-filled rooms and shared popcorn buckets.

Whether you’re a fan of cult film posters, retro art, or just like to collect tees with attitude, this piece slips into routines and moments where a wink to the dramatic feels right.

Product features
- 100% cotton (solid colors) — medium-weight 180 g/m² for year-round comfort
- Classic relaxed fit with ribbed knit crew neckline and tear-away label for itch-free wear
- Tubular knit construction (no side seams) and shoulder tape for shape retention and reduced waste
- Dual printing: detailed front print via DTG with DTF on sleeves/inner neck for crisp, lasting artwork
- Certifications and origin: Oeko-Tex certified, ethically sourced US cotton; made in Nicaragua; EU 2-year warranty

Care instructions
- Non-chlorine: bleach as needed
- Do not iron
- Do not dryclean
- Machine wash: cold (max 30C or 90F)
- Tumble dry: low heat
